lead_paragraph: Manchester City claimed a vital edge in their Champions League quarter-final tie against Paris St Germain after grabbing two away goals in a scrappy 2-2 first leg draw on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Gritty Man City Fight Back to Draw 2-2 Against PSG
